  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4997376/" class="title-link">胡因梦：你就是这本《生命之书》</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4997376"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/philosophia1979/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1137624-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/philosophia1979/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">野兽爱智慧</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-06-21"
      class="main-meta">2011-06-21 17:27:21</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
